#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/validity/algeria.rst:26
msgid "How Odoo Sign complies with Algerian regulations"
msgstr "Как Odoo Подпись соответствует алжирским нормам"

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/sign/validity/algeria.rst:28
msgid ""
"Odoo Sign ensures full compliance with the Electronic Signature Law of "
