#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/visualize_data/charts.rst:68
msgid ""
"To change the chart type, click the dropdown menu to select the desired "
"chart type."
msgstr ""
"Чтобы изменить тип диаграммы, нажмите на выпадающее меню и выберите нужный "
"тип диаграммы."

#: ../../content/applications/productivity/spreadsheet/visualize_data/charts.rst:72
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Link to Odoo menu`: to add a :ref:`clickable link <spreadsheet/"
"insert/clickable-links>` from a chart to an Odoo menu item, i.e., a specific "
"view of a model."
msgstr ""
